<workflow><wfname>Categorizing For Review</wfname>
<wfauthor>By Jennifer Mitchell</wfauthor>
<wfdescription>&lt;p&gt;In this single-class activity, students categorize statements or terms under two general headings (e.g. dividing terms into the categories of rationalism or empiricism). This activity helps students review and understand important differences between key terms and concepts we have covered. See a full description &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.saltise.ca/resources/activities/categorizing-for-review/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</wfdescription>
