<righticon>orchestration</righticon>
<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Give a quick review of key concepts used as terms before starting the review activity&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Example: When they need to break the different terms into the categories of rationalist or empiricist, review these terms and the central concepts and differences between each group.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
