<id>4</id>
<lefticon>group</lefticon>
<righticon>problem</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Collect a packet of papers and claim a section of the wall in the classroom&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use sticky tack to put the main category terms at the top on the wall, leaving space below each for the other terms&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Divide terms into the appropriate category and put them up on the wall.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Once finished, ask instructor to check&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
