<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;When a group indicates that they have finished, go and check their list&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;If they have mistakes, do not tell them what is wrong. Just tell them how many they have wrong in each side and have them continue to work on it until it is correct&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
