<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Once all groups have finished, discuss with the class:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Some of the more difficult terms&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Why difficult terms fit into a particular category&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Why terms branch between two categories, where it was included, and why&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Instruct students to keep a copy of the final version of their list. It will be useful to have for their notes. Either post a document with the answers on the course LMS or have students take a picture&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
